"Foolish child," she chuckled in the shadows. Then, thrusting her face into the light, she laughed maniacally.
Her great crooked head had offcenter eyes. A big, squashed nose on a large, fat wobbling face. A whisp of white hair tufted from her head. 
Despite her fat body, her long bony arms shot out and grabbed little red riding hood.
"I am not hungry for human food!"
